Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,回乡下老家很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒个头啦,在店里被操得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出远门去玩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能,我穷死了 好不容易才凑到回家的车票钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮好了,煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起我要去伊豆一个礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个礼拜有什么节目吗? 比如说约会之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,只有打工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 来啊,喝啊喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃这个吗? 你想吃其它的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来两盘黑轮和10串烤鸡肉串
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤鸡肉串要盐味的 黑轮要多放点芥末喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊喝啊,今天我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#21 五代危机! 一刻馆的小猫物语!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫?那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道小猫是什么吗? 就是会小声喵喵叫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在问你这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候答应帮你照顾小猫了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别说你忘记了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实答应过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么一提 难怪你昨晚莫名地拼命灌我酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的酒钱都是我出的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你的手法太肮脏了,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔,乖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住的是公寓,不可以养猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍胸脯说“包在我身上”的人是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 你是听到这家伙的名字时…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛,你怎么不早说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样,无话可说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,响子好像也很喜欢你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么要取 响子这个名字呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是管理员的迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把猫取作管理员的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系,这是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在公寓叫它的时候怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫响子不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不叫它响子的话 它不会理你的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,13点25分 开往西伊豆方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好,你要乖乖的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在外面过夜的话 至少也请打个电话回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还特地把大门的锁开着 等你回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱动,响…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气真好啊 (“响”音同“今天”)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逮到了我可不管你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗?等一下喔 我马上弄给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫罐头,猫干粮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小猫吃的 要用温汤或牛奶将干粮泡软
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦,我在弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开罐器在哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!居然在这里尿尿!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,响子,给我过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在那里也没有用 给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快点给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你叫我有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是在叫我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逃也不会躲的 到底有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有叫你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明有叫啊,你叫“响子”…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能直接叫你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我明明有听到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你没事找我罗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当然没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来,我不会打你了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便叫“响子”这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行? 这只猫叫响子,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在叫管理员的名字 听起来很不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔乖喔,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学,这是一只猫耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看喔,是母的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里啊,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这栋公寓可以养猫吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是代为照顾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向管理员打小报告好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是暂时代为照顾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一顿晚餐,不准讨价还价
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奢望的也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一客上等炸虾饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后一定要阪本付我这笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,要不要吃啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,请不要随便给它东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,吃饭罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让管理员发现就没问题了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然窝在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔,还是一只小猫耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底叫什么名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你不要大声叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家真的吓了一跳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你在叫我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你去应付一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人不太会说谎喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好,先去应付一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊,快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,幸好有你赶来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,什么事都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代突然侵犯我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你这个人怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说谎!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美你这个笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你实在太可耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说过了,我不太会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样,她在说谎,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这种谎呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄我有这么好玩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,我不是在捉弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是单身吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,竟然都干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好命了,都不用烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,阪本那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是你害的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了两三天平安无事的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样渐渐地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像对它产生了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想去上学吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是谁把小猫带到教室里来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我滚回补习班去!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代 你是不是有什么事情瞒着我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为惣一郎看到你就一直叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只是单纯地在寻求 男性之间的友谊而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有事情瞒着我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,有你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,谁打来的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾,是个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是阪本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子?它很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然直呼管理员的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,我每天晚上都抱着它睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它都会偷偷地溜到我的棉被里来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他们两人已经在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,找您五十圆,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,一之濑太太,出来买菜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?一脸笑咪咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一付纯洁乖巧的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太,到底是什么事嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听说了喔 其实不用人家说也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也是个有感情的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有半夜溜到他棉被里去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到他自己说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直叫响子响子的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,到底跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候 溜到你的棉被里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你每天晚上 都抱着管理员睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 你就老实说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把事情给我说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这房间有一股鱼腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是宠物食物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你吃这种东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,你叫的响子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是猫 为什么不一开始就讲清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛,真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,让你帮忙找猫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌,怎么取这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,来一下,快过来看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎,你要我看什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面到底有什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,话说回来 真不愧是响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你们怎么说,我都不会辞掉 一刻馆的管理员工作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母怎么这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.85,0:24:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“五代深受打击! 响子的辞职宣言”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破破烂烂的有什么关系 因为这里是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.17,0:24:34.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}那天在陌生的城市下了一场阵雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:41.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你非常在意淋湿的高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:49.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}从前你用那隐藏着 稚气的侧脸和我交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:55.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你说的话语至今仍能想起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:25:03.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}一开始就仿佛 置身电影中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:12.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你轻声细语地说着 安静的最后一幕

